<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/916544-this-looks-heart-wrenching-and-i-ve">This looks heart-wrenching, and I&#39;ve wanted to read it for a while. I tend to be quite emotional when it comes to books. Will this make me cry?</a>
</div>
